comments: I took professor Denise during the vacation, she is an awesome feminist teacher!!! Her lectures are entertaining and very informative. She is not an "easy" A, she is just very generous in the way she grades her tests and projects. There was a group project where two members did nothing at all and got full credit, choose your teammates carefully!!!
